sri-project-1 | Hydrogen Safety Research Program | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/hydrogen-safety-research-program | description:SRI has partnered with Sandia National Laboratories to provide the data necessary to ensure that hydrogen can be used safely as a transportation fuel.
sri-project-2 | Remediating Unexploded Ordnance | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/remediating-unexploded-ordnance | description:SRI has developed a novel approach to safely and efficiently render harmless weapons and ammunition that are no longer needed for military use.
